{"id": 5130, "date": "1988-08-14T11:00:37", "date_gmt": "1988-08-14T18:00:37", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=5130"}, "modified": "2026-02-23T18:06:03", "modified_gmt": "2026-02-24T02:06:03", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-jon-bon-jovi-and-bruce-springsteen-you-give-love-a-bad-name", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1988/08/14/meeting-across-the-river-jon-bon-jovi-and-bruce-springsteen-you-give-love-a-bad-name/", "title": {"rendered": "You Give Love a Bad Name"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>On January 31, 1998, Bruce joined Jon Bon Jovi on stage at the Count Basie Theater in Red Bank at a benefit concert for the memorial fund of a slain local police officer.</p>\n<p>Together they played a one-time-only rendition of Bon Jovi&#8217;s first number one hit, &#8220;You Give Love a Bad Name,&#8221; with Bruce taking lead vocals on the second verse.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0Kh1qeu3bNM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>And just because we all need to be reminded from time to time that rock stars used to look like this, here&#8217;s the original 1986 #1 hit single from <em>Slippery When Wet.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KrZHPOeOxQQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;f